PropertyCode: The Property Code field is an alphanumeric field only and is limited to 10 characters.  This field will be checked for an exact match.  If no exact match exists, the row will be marked invalid.  This is a required field for this upload.  If missing, the row will be marked inactive.
GLCode: The GL Code field is an alphanumeric field and should exactly match how it is setup in the system.  This is a required field for this upload.  If an exact match is not found, the row will be marked as invalid and skipped in the upload.
IntegrationPackage: This is a required field.  This field is a text field and will be compared for an exact match in the system.  If no exact match is found, the row will be marked invalid.  To find the integration package name, refer to the Integration Package field on any Active Property in Property Setup.
